As discussed, to ensure images based on c2cwsgiutils get up-to-date versions of Debian, we need to:
- have a branch rebuilt regularily (branch 0);
- this branch should contain the latest released version;
- a cron would pull up-to-date Docker dependencies and rebuild and push updated image to Docker hub.

